Urban worlds were release this week. They are:

```
One(1) qualification world with a combination of 3 types of artifactd (rescue Randy, phone, and, backpack) 3+3+4 for a total of 16 artifacts.

Also, three(3) simple Urban worlds with 12 artifacts each and same combination of artifacts as the qualification world.
```

```
There(3) more complex practice world will be added soon with more combination of artifacts, including two new awesome ones.
```
